title: Brown Butter Pecan Keto Ice Cream
directions: Brown butter on low heat until an amber color.
Add cream, stevia, and pecans and stir until combined together.
Whisk coconut milk and xanthan gum into brown butter mixture, then place in ice cream machine.
Follow manufacturers instructions for ice cream machine.
ingredients: 1 1/2 cups Unsweetened Coconut Milk (from the carton)
